---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
    <style>
      .title {
        margin-bottom: 1em;
        padding: 1em 0;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .title h1 {
        line-height: 1;
      }
      h2 {
        font-size: 1.95em;
      }
    </style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
      <div class="title">
        <h1>About</h1>
        <hr />
      </div>

      <p>Working on iOS apps and tools since 2023, I've contributed to projects that have impacted over 100,000 users worldwide. Always concerned with the user experience, I prioritize usability and high retention rates.</p>

      <h2>Work Experience</h2>

      <p>- <strong>iOS Engineer</strong> at <strong>BRQ Digital Solutions</strong> (November 2023 - Present)</p>
      <p>BRQ Digital Solutions, a leader in digital transformation in Brazil, delivers end-to-end development from concept to digital product, operating globally to drive business growth through technology.</p>
